The '''Baragwin heavy repeating blaster''' was a model of [[Repeating blaster/Legends|repeating blaster]] that was manufactured by the [[Baragwin/Legends|Baragwin]], who were known as gifted weaponsmiths. Such repeating blasters were highly upgradeable and packed a heavy punch; as such, they were quite pricey. If upgraded, it was said that these weapons could set durasteel on fire for a short time.<ref name="KOTOR">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''</ref>

